{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_37","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated `library-new-request` job for `org.jboss.xnio:xnio-nio:3.8.7.Final` failed. Preserved work is available on branch `https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-1538-library-new-request-org.jboss.xnio-xnio-nio-3.8.7.Final-61c347e1`.\n\nThe most likely failing stage was the test-generation/native-image verification loop. The run first failed in `nativeTestCompile` with `Substitution target for org.wildfly.common.Substitutions$Target_GraalDirectives is not loaded` (`human-intervention-logs/org.jboss.xnio:xnio-nio:3.8.7.Final/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-08-00-388923Z.log`). After that, repeated `nativeTest` runs failed with `ExceptionInInitializerError` caused by `Invalid logger interface org.xnio._private.Messages (implementation not found...)`, which points to missing reflection metadata for the generated JBoss Logging implementations (`human-intervention-logs/org.jboss.xnio:xnio-nio:3.8.7.Final/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-09-54-503012Z.log`, `.../gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-12-03-625294Z.log`, `.../gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-16-06-899804Z.log`, `.../gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-16-28-548135Z.log`). One intermediate test iteration also introduced a failing JVM test, `compressionChannelsRoundTripDataThroughHalfDuplexPipe()`, with `java.io.IOException: Stream ended before the expected bytes were read` (`.../gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-14-06-224158Z.log` and `.../gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-15-03-256197Z.log`).\n\nThe preserved branch also contains a follow-up metadata-fix pass: `human-intervention-logs/org.jboss.xnio:xnio-nio:3.8.7.Final/metadata-fix/codex.log` shows a successful local reproduce/fix/verify run after adding reflection entries for `org.xnio._private.Messages_$logger` and `org.xnio.nio.Log_$logger`, and the final reruns are green in `.../gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-19-48-819886Z.log` and `.../gradle-test-2026-05-20T13-20-07-890271Z.log`. However, the metrics still recorded the overall strategy as `failure` after 6 iterations (`stats/org.jboss.xnio/xnio-nio/3.8.7.Final/execution-metrics.json`), and there was no useful dynamic-access signal (`0/0`).\n\nNext steps:\n1. Review the preserved branch changes, especially the generated test, the direct `wildfly-common` dependency, and `metadata/org.jboss.xnio/xnio-nio/3.8.7.Final/reachability-metadata.json`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.jboss.xnio:xnio-nio:3.8.7.Final` from the preserved branch in a clean environment.\n3. If that stays green, open a fresh PR from the preserved branch; if not, continue from the native-image logger failure and the `wildfly-common` substitution incompatibility above."}}
